      *                  * Se Up                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad accettazioni                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-ric-sel-100.
       acc-ric-sel-999.
           exit.

