                     go to tdo-ric-sel-250.
           if        rr-dat-ini           not  = zero
                     go to tdo-ric-sel-250.
           move      "Manca la data iniziale !                          
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     tdo-ric-sel-900.
       tdo-ric-sel-250.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su data finale da stampare                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
